{"id": 2238, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今你如何定义娱乐？", "description": "看电影刷剧无疑是娱乐，但逛商场是娱乐吗？健身、刷手机呢？你觉得需要包含哪些要素才算娱乐?（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 1302, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803201513450bTsR6Il1ifXOKxn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 271872, "content": "和熟悉的人说上两句消遣的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291000}, {"id": 271873, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144874}, {"id": 271874, "content": "不需要动脑子的活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291615}, {"id": 271877, "content": "工作之外，好自己喜欢的事都是娱乐，无论游戏还是逛街", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185153}, {"id": 271879, "content": "娱乐就是做自己喜欢的事情啊。如果你觉得你喜欢工作，那么工作也是一种娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291619}, {"id": 272391, "content": "工作以外的能让自我心情愉悦的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293686}, {"id": 273159, "content": "独自一人，清清静静的看剧或者其他什么都行，不必在乎任何人的看法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297980}, {"id": 271880, "content": "寓教于乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284811}, {"id": 274952, "content": "找女个女朋友然后睡一觉☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309794}, {"id": 271881, "content": "有兴趣做的事情大概在我眼里都是娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264890}, {"id": 271882, "content": "大概就是刷微博知乎豆瓣贴吧抖音好奇心日报吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281633}, {"id": 271883, "content": "笑使我感到娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292003}, {"id": 275724, "content": "与严肃相对的概念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314940}, {"id": 271885, "content": "麻醉至死之物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168033}, {"id": 271888, "content": "让人忘了现实世界的烦忧，全身心投入，感到幸福感和成就感的体验，比如游戏，电影，小说", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265413}, {"id": 272400, "content": "以为自己没动脑子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240282}, {"id": 271890, "content": "能真的开心就是娱乐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475929}, {"id": 273426, "content": "哗众取宠，形式大于内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894397}, {"id": 272147, "content": "做回真实的自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292996}, {"id": 271895, "content": "娱乐不是简单的一些无聊的嬉笑怒骂，而是得让人从心底放松而又有所得～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232483}, {"id": 271896, "content": "呈现生活中不经意却有趣的事，或者是约定俗成大家喜爱的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900556}, {"id": 271897, "content": "steam理财了解一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945752}, {"id": 272665, "content": "什么都不做，思想处于空定状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269251}, {"id": 271898, "content": "娱乐与我而言大抵是和三两好友约去撸串看电影.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275839}, {"id": 271899, "content": "过程 ＞ 结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287419}, {"id": 271900, "content": "福尔摩斯说过，改变工作内容就是最大的快乐！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843126}, {"id": 271901, "content": "让自己心情愉悦的，就是娱乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699722}, {"id": 271902, "content": "做内个。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292039}, {"id": 271903, "content": "能让脑子放空的任何事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677618}, {"id": 271904, "content": "做起来觉得人生是有意义的事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292041}, {"id": 272160, "content": "打发时间，发泄情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013567}, {"id": 271905, "content": "日常生活的配菜，可能是营养健康，色香味俱全，也可能会含有地沟油成分，危害身心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269743}, {"id": 271906, "content": "愉悦身心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292043}, {"id": 271907, "content": "身心放松，享乐时光?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525030}, {"id": 271908, "content": "我只能举反例，譬如，定义“娱乐”这件事情，一点都不娱乐，但我输入以上文字，是娱乐，笑脸.jpg", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145706}, {"id": 271909, "content": "感觉享受，没有浪费时间的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221114}, {"id": 271910, "content": "不以挣钱为目的的都是娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034688}, {"id": 272166, "content": "一般来说，在学习工作除外每天的娱乐就是和几个挚友聊聊天南海北，或者刷刷微博，自己开心是最重要的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293036}, {"id": 271911, "content": "泡杯下午茶，坐在阳台下 晒太阳 看着电视剧 看看书  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292056}, {"id": 271913, "content": "可以使自己发自内心的快乐的事情！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291686}, {"id": 271914, "content": "愉悦且有品质的时间消磨活动。事后不会觉得这段时间没用来学习or工作而感到后悔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866970}, {"id": 271916, "content": "重点在乐了就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217432}, {"id": 271917, "content": "可以让大脑完全放空，可以不用看手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001373}, {"id": 273197, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298073}, {"id": 271918, "content": "能让自己感到放松，心情愉悦的时刻，可能是一杯酒，一朵花。甚至是一句话，一个眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292109}, {"id": 271919, "content": "我认为各种不同的方式（当然安全合法）达到舒适放松的状态就是娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291775}, {"id": 271921, "content": "我认为，娱乐＝放松，什么时候是放松的？当你碰到一个你了解的东西或事情时，你不会感到丝毫的紧张，不怯场，那便是放松。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292116}, {"id": 272946, "content": "不用工作也可以收钱的包租婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297034}, {"id": 273458, "content": "能让我觉得开心得没什么包袱又让人心情舒畅的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179644}, {"id": 271923, "content": "不费脑子，躺着也能玩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292131}]}